petitioner%20and%20under%20the%20undue%20influence%20of%20US%20agencies%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20extradite%20the%20petitioner%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BForced%20To%20Eat%20Pork%2C%20Beef%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20in%20the%20first%2010-11%20days%20of%20prison%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20was%20offered%20only%20pork%20and%20beef%2C%20which%20he%20could%20not%20eat%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdevout%20Hindu%20and%20vegetarian%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20authorities%20were%20informed%2C%20they%20refused%20to%20give%20him%20vegetarian%20food..%20was%20forced%20to%20eat%20food%20that%20violates...%20most%20basic%20human%20rights%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20Not%20Contact%20Family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20was%20allegedly%20also%20not%20allowed%20to%20contact%20his%20family%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3B...%20petitioner%20was%20told%20by%20local%20authorities%20in%20Prague%20(this%20would%20be%20possible)%20only%20after%20US%20authorities%20approve%20of%20him%20making%20calls%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20he%20was%20allegedly%20allowed%20to%20meet%20an%20Indian%20official%20was%20July%2019%20-%20nearly%2020%20days%20after%20his%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20detention%2C%20and%20contact%20with%20family%20was%20only%20allowed%20after%20the%20Prague%20High%20Court%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20Case%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20is%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun%2C%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20who%20holds%20American-Canadian%20citizenship.%20The%20'hitman'%20was%20an%20undercover%20US%20federal%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-nikhil-gupta-man-charged-in-failed-plot-to-kill-khalistan-terrorist-4623848%5C%22%20