ems%20a%20deliberate%20effort%20to%20keep%20me%20out%2C%20even%20when%20franchises%20have%20opted%20for%20other%20performers%20with%20inferior%20numbers%20than%20me.%20But%20when%20everything%20is%20pre-planned%20so%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter.%20I%20don't%20know%20whose%20responsibility%20it%20is%20to%20get%20top%20domestic%20performers%20in%20the%20PSL%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20heartfelt%20goodbye!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7NdjpCXjeR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7NdjpCXjeR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ahmad%20Shahzad%20(%40iamAhmadshahzad)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FiamAhmadshahzad%2Fstatus%2F1735540788170227918%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahzad%20suggested%20that%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20some%20conspiracy%20in%20the%20PSL%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20him%20getting%20ignored%20by%20all%206%20franchises.%20He%20has%20vowed%20to%20reveal%20the%20truth%20soon%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20exactly%20know%20the%20reasons%20why%20I'm%20not%20made%20part%20of%20the%20PSL%20-%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20and%20my%20fans%20will%20know%20it%20very%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20parting%20ways%20and%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20for%20my%20own%20self%20respect.%20I've%20never%20played%20for%20money%20and%20will%20never%20do%20it.%20While%20many%20chose%20international%20leagues%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20grind%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20to%20prove%20my%20love%20for%20the%20game%2C%20and%20to%20wear%20the%20Green%20Flag%20again.%20I'm%20taking%20this%20decision%20keeping%20money%20out%20of%20it%20(was%20offered%20several%20contracts%20to%20play%20leagues%20yet%20chose%20Pakistan).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20play%20the%20PSL%20again%20with%20these%206%20teams.%20It%20seems%20like%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20to%20keep%20me%20away%20from%20PSL%2C%20and%20all%20franchises%20have%20shaken%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLastly%2C%20I'm%20thankful%20to%20all%20the%20support%20I've%20received%20from%20my%20fans%20across%20the%20world.%20I%20can%20only%20assure%20one%20thing%20and%20that's%20never%20giving%20in%20to%20unfair%20demands%20or%20accept%20anything%20which%20lets%20my%20country%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20know%20is%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%20being%20patriotic%20and%20putting%20your%20nation%20first%20goes%20against%20you.%20I'm%20thankful%20to%20my%20Allah%20that%20I%20always%20stood%20firm%20on%20my%20moral%20responsibilities%20and%20have%20never%20let%20myself%2C%20my%20family%20and%20my%20country%20down.%20If%20that's%20the%20price%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20honesty%20and%20dedication%2C%20it's%20really%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20doing%20it.%20Pakistan%20Zindabad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702622880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq7fgke1o_ahmad-shahzad-twitter_625x300_15_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdeliberate-attempt-to-keep-me-out-pakistan-star-ahmad-shahzad-quits-psl-out-of-self-respect-4677923%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20cricketer%20Ahmad%20Shahzad%20decided%20to%20quit%20the%20PSL%20after%20failing%20to%20get%20picked%20in%20the%20draft%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdeliberate-attempt-to-keep-me-out-pakistan-star-ahmad-shahzad-quits-psl-out-of-self-respect-4677923%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdeliberate-attempt-to-keep-me-out-pakistan-star-ahmad-shahzad-quits-psl-out-of-self-respect-4677923%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdeliberate-attempt-to-keep-me-out-pakistan-star-ahmad-shahzad-quits-psl-out-of-self-respect-4677923%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won't%20Control%20What%20a%20Judge%20Does%20With%20a%20Matter%20Listed%20in%20Front%20of%20Them%3A%20CJI%20Chandrachud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20limelight%20recently%20for%20the%20allegedly%20arbitrary%20manner%20in%20which%20cases%20were%20being%20assigned%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2014)%20said%20he%20cannot%20control%20how%20a%20judge%20handles%20a%20case%20listed%20before%20them%20and%20will%20not%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20refused%20to%20intervene%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20listing%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Satyendar%20Jain%E2%80%99s%20petition%20for%20bail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20before%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fwill-not-control-the-judge-cji-refuses-to-defer-hearing-on-satyendar-jains-bail-plea-listed-before-another-bench-2810934%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Jain%2C%20said%20in%20front%20of%20the%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20bench%20that%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20deferred.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20case%20had%20originally%20been%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20A.S.%20Bopanna%2C%20and%20was%20later%20moved%20to%20Justice%20Trivedi%E2%80%99s%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20justice%20refused%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20control%20what%20the%20judge%20is%20doing%20in%20the%20matter%20listed%20before%20her.%20The%20judge%20who%20has%20the%20case%20will%20decide.%20I%20cannot.%20I%20cannot%20take%20a%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%206%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20on%20the%20question%20of%20case%20listing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20personally%20come%20across%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20listed%20before%20various%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20upon%20first%20listing%20and%2F%20or%20in%20which%20notice%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20being%20taken%20away%20from%20those%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20and%20listed%20before%20other%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches.%20Despite%20first%20coram%20being%20available%20the%20matters%20are%20being%20listed%20before%20a%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20in%20which%20second%20coram%20presides.%20Matters%20listed%20before%20Court%20No.%202%2C%204%2C%206%2C%207%20amongst%20others%20have%20been%20shifted%20out%20and%20listed%20before%20other%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Benches%20in%20clear%20disregard%20of%20the%20Rules%2C%20the%20Handbook%20on%20Practice%20and%20Office%20Procedure%20referred%20above%20and%20established%20Practice%20and%20Convention.%20Curiously%2C%20the%20Seniority%20of%20the%20first%20coram%20is%20also%20being%20ignored%20in%20doing%20so.%20Our%20attention%20is%20also%20been%20drawn%20by%20esteemed%20Colleagues%20at%20the%20Bar%2C%20Seniors%2C%20and%20Advocates%20on%20Record%20(AoRs)%2C%20about%20various%20cases%20in%20which%20they%20have%20appeared%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20later%20the%20matters%20being%20listed%20before%20different%20Benches.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20proper%20for%20me%20to%20enumerate%20these%20matters%20as%20many%20of%20them%20are%20pending%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-registry-isnt-listing-cases-the-way-it-is-supposed-to-a-letter-to-the-cji%5C%22%3EDave%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fprashant-bhushan-writes-to-sc-registrar-on-arbitrary-allocation-of-cases-to-justice-bela-m-trivedi%5C%22%3Ewrote%20to%20the%20registrar%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20questioning%20the%20way%20in%20which%20sensitive%20cases%20were%20being%20transferred%20to%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Trivedi.%20Bhushan%20specifically%20expressed%20concern%20about%20a%20batch%20of%20matters%20challenging%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20cases%20coming%20up%20before%20Justice%20Trivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fcontrary-to-sc-s-rules-of-assignment-at-least-8-politically-sensitive-cases-moved-to-one-judge-in-4-months-65713ae124602%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20highlighted%20the%20news%20about%20cases%20being%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20Justice%20Trivedi%2C%20reporting%20that%20%E2%80%9CAn%20analysis%20of%20eight%20politically%20sensitive%20cases%20shows%20they%20were%20moved%20to%20Justice%20Bela%20M%20Trivedi%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20the%20past%20four%20months%2C%20even%20though%20the%20rules%20of%20assignment%20say%20they%20should%20remain%20with%20the%20senior%20judge%20or%20before%20a%20judge%20hearing%20a%20similar%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702622493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwont-control-what-a-judge-does-with-a-matter-listed-in-front-of-them-cji-chandrachud%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20in%20the%20limelight%20recently%20for%20the%20allegedly%20arbitrary%20manner%20in%20which%20cases%20were%20being%20assigned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%