20days%20of%20counting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unprecedented%20haul%20marks%20the%20largest%20single%20seizure%20ever%20made%20by%20any%20investigative%20agency%20in%20India%2C%20shattering%20all%20the%20previous%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20massive%20cash%20recovery%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20is%20now%20using%20high-tech%20gadgets%20to%20look%20for%20any%20gold%20jewellery%20that%20could%20be%20hidden%20below%20the%20ground%20at%20the%20premises%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Sahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20I-T%20teams%20are%20using%20the%20geo%20surveillance%20system%20-%20which%20helps%20detect%20the%20jewellery%20and%20other%20valuables%20hidden%20below%20the%20ground%20easily%20-%20at%20the%20two%20houses%20of%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%20in%20Ranchi%20and%20Lohardaga%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20cash.%20The%20department%20is%20high-tech%2C%20so%20you%20can%20expect%20the%20latest%20available%20technology%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20searches%20to%20find%20moe%20gold%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20an%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20raids%20were%20launched%20on%20December%206%20on%20charges%20of%20tax%20evasion%20and%20%26quot%3Boff-the-book%26quot%3B%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I-T%20Department%20suspects%20that%20the%20massive%20cache%20of%20cash%20unearthed%20during%20raids%20on%20Boudh%20Distilleries%20and%20associated%20entities%20represents%20unaccounted%20income%20generated%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20country%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20launched%20a%20powerful%20counter-offensive%2C%20aiming%20at%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20declared%20that%20their%20prior%20accusations%20of%20the%20government%20misusing%20investigative%20agencies%20are%20now%20exposed%20as%20mere%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%2C%26quot%3B%20driven%20by%20their%20fear%20of%20being%20held%20accountable%20for%20their%20alleged%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20assured%20the%20public%20that%20%26quot%3Blooted%20money%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20returned.%20The%20PM%20shared%20a%20Hindi%20newspaper%20report%20showing%20the%20mountains%20of%20cash%20recovered%20by%20the%20income%20tax%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20connected%20with%20the%20businesses%20in%20any%20way%20and%20that%20the%20MP%20should%20explain%20the%20cash%20and%20its%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702621440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fji0boflk_dheeraj-sahu-1200_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhiraj-sahu-income-tax-raids-odisha-rs-353-crore-cash-haul-in-searches-against-congress-mp-officials-go-hi-tech-to-find-hidden-gold-4677443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cash%20seizure%20in%20the%20tax%20searches%20against%20an%20Odisha-based%20distillery%20company%20owned%20by%20Congress%20MP%20Dhiraj%20Kumar%20Sahu's%20family%2C%20reached%20Rs%20353.5%20crore%20on%20Sunday%20after%20five%20days%20of%20counting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhiraj-sahu-income-tax-raids-odisha-rs-353-crore-cash-haul-in-searches-against-congress-mp-officials-go-hi-tech-to-find-hidden-gold-4677443%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhiraj-sahu-income-tax-raids-odisha-rs-353-crore-cash-haul-in-searches-against-congress-mp-officials-go-hi-tech-to-find-hidden-gold-4677443%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhiraj-sahu-income-tax-raids-odisha-rs-353-crore-cash-haul-in-searches-against-congress-mp-officials-go-hi-tech-to-find-hidden-gold-467