cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Ode%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Ad-Hoc%E2%80%99%20Teachers%20of%20Ramjas%20English%20Department%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15112300%2FScreenshot-2023-12-15-at-11.22.22%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%20as%20the%20practice%20of%20freedom%E2%80%94as%20opposed%20to%20education%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20the%20practice%20of%20domination%E2%80%94denies%20that%20man%20is%20abstract%2C%20isolated%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eindependent%2C%20and%20unattached%20to%20the%20world%3B%20it%20also%20denies%20that%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eworld%20exists%20as%20a%20reality%20apart%20from%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20Paulo%20Freire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPedagogy%20of%20the%20Oppressed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ramjas%20English%20Department%2C%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%9CRED%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20brick%20walls%2C%20the%20colour%20of%20passion%2C%20love%20and%20vigour%20%E2%80%93%20has%20now%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-removal-of-ramjas-colleges-ad-hoc-teachers-raises-concerns-about-dus-academic-standards%5C%22%3Emade%20to%20lose%20eight%20of%20its%20ten%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cad-hoc%E2%80%9D%20teachers.%20This%20development%20isn%E2%80%99t%20new%20for%20anyone%20aware%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20over%20these%20past%20few%20years%2C%20and%20the%20precarious%20lives%20that%20%E2%80%9Cad-hocism%E2%80%9D%20creates%20for%20many%20qualified%2C%20deserving%20and%20passionate%20teachers.%20Much%20has%20been%20said%20about%20how%20this%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Contract%20Labour%20(Regulation%20and%20Abolition)%20Act%20(CLRA%20Act)%2C%201970.%20Appointment%20rules%20permit%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20%E2%80%9Cad-hoc%E2%80%9D%20positions%20only%20by%20conditions%20necessitated%20in%20contingent%20situations%20(death%2C%20leave%2C%20etc.)%2C%20and%20not%20to%20prolong%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20the%20university.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20leave%20the%20legalities%20to%20better%20minds%20and%20limit%20%E2%80%93%20or%20perhaps%20broaden%20%E2%80%93%20the%20discourse%20to%20demonstrate%20who%20these%20people%20are%3A%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20unnamed%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20go%20on%20labouring%20under%20dire%20situations%20to%20bring%20education%20to%20classrooms%20that%20are%20packed%2C%20often%20with%20more%20students%20than%20there%20are%20provisions%20to%20sit%3B%20ones%20who%20make%20it%20a%20pleasure%20to%20sit%20in%20a%20class%20even%20in%20the%20summers%20of%20Delhi%2C%20in%20places%20where%20sometimes%20even%20fans%20don%E2%80%99t%20work!%20They%20patiently%20answer%20questions%2C%20engage%20with%20the%20curiosity%20and%20agility%20of%20youth%20%E2%80%93%20all%20the%20while%20living%20their%20tumultuous%20lives%20which%20do%20not%20allow%20the%20luxuries%20that%20a%20student%20enjoys.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20went%20to%20Ramjas%20English%20Department%20first%20%E2%80%93%20only%20eight%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Bhubaneswar%20in%20Orissa%2C%20I%20was%20greeted%20by%20these%20professors%20with%20joy.%20With%20their%20resplendent%20mirth%2C%20they%20made%20the%20unfamiliar%20familiar.%20I%20knew%20nothing%20about%20Delhi%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20labour%20dynamics%20in%20the%20University.%20I%20would%20see%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20professors%20alongside%20the%20%E2%80%9Cad-hocs%E2%80%9D%20and%20never%20for%20once%20understand%20the%20difference%20%E2%80%93%20both%20taught%20us%2C%20both%20required%20degrees%2C%20what%20separated%20them%3F%20This%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20for%20the%20naive%20perceptions%20of%20a%20young%20student%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%2C%20and%20I%20was%20no%20exception.%20Slowly%2C%20and%20gradually%2C%20alongside%20classes%20on%20labour%2C%20or%20reading%20about%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdivision%20of%20labour%E2%80%9D%20in%20class%20and%20mingling%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cad-hocs%E2%80%9D%2C%20one%20would%20open%20one%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20to%20inequalities%20that%20were%20present%20both%20outside%20and%20inside%20the%20classroom.%20The%20University%20was%20a%20space%20of%20abject%20inequalities%20based%20on%20gender%2C%20caste%20and%20class.%20The%20irony%3A%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cad-hoc%E2%80%9D%20teachers%20who%20would%20teach%20us%20about%20inequalities%20that%20perhaps%20bore%20the%20sharpest%20repercussions%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fad-hoc-teachers-at-delhi-university-from-the-frying-pan-into-the-fire%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ad-hoc%E2%80%99%20Teachers%20at%20Delhi%20University%3A%20From%20the%20Frying%20Pan%20into%20the%20Fire%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20professors%20in%20Ramjas%20English%20Department%20comfortably%20ushered%20in%20not%20only%20me%20but%20many%20others%20who%20came%20from%20different%20circumstances%2C%20different%20cities%2C%20and%20wholly%20different%20worlds%20and%20worldviews%3A%20a%20bunch%20of%20young%20men%20and%20women%2C%20who%20had%20nothing%20in%20common%2C%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20new%20threshold%20of%20education%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%20of%20the%20word.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20professors%20had%20to%20finish%20their%20doctoral%20research%2C%20write%20papers%2C%20present%20in%20conferences%2C%20and%20yet%20miraculously%20also%20had%20time%20for%20that%20one%20extra%20reading%20that%20a%20student%20like%20me%20would%20have%20requested%2C%20or%20find%20time%20for%20lunch%20at%20D-School%20Canteen%20to%20give%20a%20serious%20answer%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20treated%20the%20student%20with%20an%20air%20of%20profundity%2C%20made%20each%20student%20a%20citizen%2C%20an%20individual%2C%20a%20person%20in%20our%20own%20right.%20They%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20department%20even%20though%20their%20achievements%20could%20take%20them%20to%20more%20secure%20places%20because%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20give%20their%20long%2C%20productive%20youth%20to%20their%20own%20University%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20them%20are%20former%20students%20of%20Delhi%20University.%20Their%20passion%20for%20teaching%20and%20building%20required%20much%20patience%2C%20and%20to%20instill%20a%20critical%2C%20thoughtful%20mind%20in%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20these%20years%2C%20as%20time%20passed%20and%20situations%20changed%2C%20I%20have%20now%20come%20to%20be%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20table%3A%20be%20a%20teacher%20as%20well%20as%20a%20doctoral%20student%2C%20and%2C%20with%20renewed%20vigour%2C%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20them%20to%20learn%2C%20once%20again%2C%20how%20to%20teach.%20I%20have%20recollected%20how%20they%20have%20never%20lost%20patience%20with%20the%20naivete%20of%20our%20questions%2C%20our%20empty%20rebellions%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%20that%20are%20lost%20on%20us%20today%2C%20and%20not%20once%20punished%20us%20for%20disagreeing%20with%20them.%20They%20have%2C%20with%20utmost%20respectability%2C%20taught%20us%20to%20form%20our%20own%20opinions%2C%20warned%20us%20never%20to%20close%20our%20eyes%20to%20reason%20and%20dialogue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20expanse%20of%20Ramjas%E2%80%99%20lawns%2C%20corridors%2C%20cafeterias%2C%20and%20auditoriums%2C%20they%20have%20persevered%20to%20enhance%20our%20minds%2C%20showed%20us%20the%20delights%20of%20values%2