ervice%26quot%3B%2C%20Garland%20said%20that%20her%20commitment%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpursuit%20of%20justice%20and%20relentless%20focus%20on%20bringing%20people%20together%20to%20find%20common%20ground%20made%20her%20an%20incredibly%20effective%20leader%20in%20dealing%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20challenges%20facing%20the%20American%20people.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe%20played%20an%20integral%20role%20in%20the%20department's%20efforts%20to%20combat%20violent%20crime%20and%20gun%20violence%20and%20to%20support%20the%20victims%20of%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Garland%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20the%20Justice%20Department%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highest-ranking%20Indian-American%20in%20the%20department%2C%20Ms%20Gupta%20spearheaded%20issues%20from%20building%20police-community%20trust%20to%20safeguarding%20reproductive%20freedom%2C%20increasing%20support%20for%20victims%20of%20gun%20violence%20and%20other%20crimes%2C%20promoting%20competition%20and%20economic%20opportunity%2C%20and%20expanding%20community%20violence%20intervention%20programmes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20DoJ's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20supervised%20the%20department's%20civil%20litigating%20divisions%2C%20grantmaking%20components%2C%20Office%20for%20Access%20to%20Justice%2C%20Office%20of%20Information%20Policy%2C%20Community%20Relations%20Service%2C%20United%20States%20Trustees%20Programme%2C%20and%20Foreign%20Claims%20Settlement%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20acting%20assistant%20attorney%20general%20and%20one%20of%20America's%20best-known%20and%20most%20respected%20civil%20rights%20attorneys%2C%20Ms%20Gupta%20chairs%20the%20department's%20Reproductive%20Rights%20and%20Opioid%20Epidemic%20Civil%20Litigation%20Task%20Forces%20and%20is%20leading%20its%20work%20to%20combat%20unjust%20and%20unlawful%20fines%20and%20fees%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20President%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20Leadership%20Conference%20on%20Civil%20and%20Human%20Rights%2C%20the%20oldest%20and%20the%20largest%20coalition%20of%20non-partisan%20civil%20rights%20organisations%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20according%20to%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Deputy%20Legal%20Director%20and%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Justice%20at%20the%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20(ACLU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20graduated%20from%20Yale%20University%20and%20received%20her%20law%20degree%20from%20New%20York%20University%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20where%20she%20later%20taught%20a%20civil%20rights%20litigation%20clinic%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702618740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Fvanita-gupta_650x400_81470994671.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-vanita-gupta-to-step-down-as-us-associate-attorney-general-4677635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Associate%20Attorney%20General%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Indian-American%20Vanita%20Gupta%2C%20will%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post%20in%20February%202024%2C%20an%20official%20release%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-vanita-gupta-to-step-down-as-us-associate-attorney-general-4677635%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-vanita-gupta-to-step-down-as-us-associate-attorney-general-4677635%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-vanita-gupta-to-step-down-as-us-associate-attorney-general-4677635%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22