amp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmahindra-finance-to-foray-into-life-health-and-general-insurance-123121500178_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmahindra-finance-to-foray-into-life-health-and-general-insurance-123121500178_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20people%20becoming%20top%20executives%20at%20Fortune%20100%20companies%20are%20getting%20older%20and%20older%3A%20study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222119%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20average%20age%20of%20Fortune%20100%20C-suite%20executives%20is%20now%2057%20years-old%2C%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20in%201980.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657bc32f50edbc52a8649617%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20average%20age%20of%20Fortune%20100%20C-suite%20executives%20is%20now%2057%20years-old%2C%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20in%201980.%3Cp%3EYuri_Arcurs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20average%20age%20of%20C-suite%20executives%20at%20Fortune%20100%20companies%20is%2057%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EC-suite%20executives%20had%20been%20getting%20younger%20since%201980%2C%20but%20that's%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20C-suite%20is%20%26quot%3Bolder%2C%20with%20broader%20industry%20experience%20and%20increasingly%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Wharton%20professor%20Peter%20Cappelli.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20demographic%20shift%20occurring%20among%20today's%20top%20executives%3A%20they're%20older%2C%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20female.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania's%20Wharton%20school%20and%20Madrid's%20IE%20University%2C%20published%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fpromoted-executive-age-64b6e169%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20age%20of%20C-suite%20executives%20at%20Fortune%20100%20companies%20is%2057%2C%20the%20same%20as%20it%20was%20four%20decades%20ago.%20The%20study%20looked%20at%20C-suite%20leaders%20at%20these%20companies%20from%201980%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20reversal%20of%20a%20long%20trend.%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Peter%20Cappelli%2C%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%20and%20a%20professor%20at%20Penn's%20Wharton%20School%20of%20Management.%20The%20average%20age%20of%20C-suite%20executives%20was%20trending%20downwards%20after%201980%2C%20to%20an%20average%20age%20of%2051%20in%202001%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20C-suite%20executives%20at%20Fortune%20100%20companies%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20jumped%20across%20industries%2C%20and%20have%20backgrounds%20in%20law%20or%20finance.%20They%20were%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20women%2C%20compared%20to%20levels%20seen%20in%201980.%20In%202021%2C%2028%25%20of%20Fortune%20100%20C-suite%20leaders%20were%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere's%20the%20face%20of%20the%20new%20C-suite%3A%20older%2C%20with%20broader%20industry%20experience%20and%20increasingly%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Cappelli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiversity%20has%20long%20been%20an%20issue%20within%20America's%20top%20boardrooms%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fpages%2Fabout-deloitte%2Farticles%2Fpress-releases%2Fnew-data-reveals-opportunity-for-growth-on-fortune-500-boards-to-be-more-representative-of-the-us-population.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20half%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20board%20seats%20at%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20being%20held%20by%20white%20men%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20consulting%20firm%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECappelli's%20study%20found%20that%20C-suite%20executives%20at%20America's%20biggest%20companies%20also%20tend%20to%20be%20older%20Gen%20X-ers%20%E2%80%94%20those%20born%20between%201965%20and%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20age%20trend%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F06%2F08%2Fhow-old-fortune-500-ceo-gen-x-keanu-reeves-musk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFortune%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20companies%2C%20where%20CEOs%20had%20an%20average%20age%20of%2057.7%20as%20of%20June%2C%20according%20to%20Fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spencerstuart.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2F2023%2Fseptember%2Fusbi%2F2023_us_spencer_stuart_board_index.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpencer%20Stuart's%20Board%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202023%20found%20that%20the%20average%20age%20of%20independent%20directors%20in%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20was%2063.%20Further%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20younger%2C%20next-generation%20directors%20%E2%80%94%20those%20aged%2050%20and%20under%20%E2%80%94%20appointed%20to%20these%20boards%20in%202023%20declined%20to%2011%25%2C%20down%20from%2018%25%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffortune-100-c-suite-executives-getting-older-trend-study-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702614239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657bc6ed50edbc52a8649641%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffortune-100-c-suite-executives-getting-older-trend-study-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20C-suite%20is%20%26quot%3Bolder%2C%20with%20broader%20industry%20experience%20and%20increasingly%20female%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Wharton%20professor%20Peter%20Cappelli.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffortune-100-c-suite-executives-getting-older-trend-study-2023-12%22%2