80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Frevealing-allegations-on-nijjar-death-meant-to-put-a-chill-on-india-trudeau-says-1.6683983%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3ECanadian%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trudeau%20expressed%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20unveil%20evidence%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20the%20US%20when%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20reach%20those%20points%20in%20the%20investigation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20US%20investigators%20initiated%20their%20attempted%20murder%20probe%20much%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCanada%20is%20investigating%20a%20murder%20and%20there%20are%20different%20stakes%20involved%20in%20that%20and%20our%20justice%20system%20has%20different%20processes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20is%20unfolding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20attempted%20assassination%20plot%20on%20a%20US-based%20Sikh%20separatist%20as%20laid%20out%20in%20court%20papers%20filed%20by%20US%20investigators.%20The%20Canadian%20government%20has%20accused%20Indian%20government%20agents%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20June%2018%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20declared%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20India%20had%20stopped%20all%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20and%20demanded%20parity%20in%20diplomatic%20representation%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%2041%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20such%20strong%20reaction%20from%20India%20to%20the%20US%20administration%20about%20the%20plot%20allegations.%20Instead%2C%20New%20Delhi%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20of%20inquiry%20after%20the%20US%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20mentioned%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20announcement%20on%20September%2018%20in%20the%20lower%20chamber%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20because%20he%20anticipated%20that%20the%20information%20would%20inevitably%20be%20leaked%20by%20the%20media.%20The%20%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20already%20ready%20to%20report%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20his%20public%20statement%20followed%20weeks%20of%20%E2%80%9Cquiet%20diplomacy%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20included%20a%20private%2016-minute%20conversation%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20admitted%20that%20those%20talks%20were%20not%20constructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20that%20all%20the%20quiet%20diplomacy%20and%20all%20the%20measures%20that%20we%20put%20in%20%E2%80%93%20and%20ensured%20that%20our%20security%20services%20put%20in%20to%20keep%20people%20safe%20in%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20needed%20a%20further%20level%20of%20deterrence%2C%20perhaps%20of%20saying%20publicly%20and%20loudly%20that%20we%20know%2C%20or%20we%20have%20credible%20reasons%20to%20believe%2C%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20behind%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20therefore%20put%20a%20chill%20on%20them%20continuing%20or%20considering%20doing%20anything%20like%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20additionally%20mentioned%20that%20Canada%20alerted%20India%20to%20the%20inevitable%20disclosure%20of%20the%20information.%20He%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20was%20told%20that%20while%20Canada%20had%20managed%20to%20keep%20things%20on%20the%20diplomatic%20level%20till%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20it%20did%20not%20have%20much%20control%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702612316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20184825%2Fimage-1329.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwill-disclose-evidence-on-indian-govts-alleged-involvement-in-assassination-like-the-us-did-trudeau%