rds%2Fnews%2Faacta-international-awards-nominations-barbenheimer-killers-of-the-flower-moon-1235840625%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fawards%2Fnews%2Faacta-international-awards-nominations-barbenheimer-killers-of-the-flower-moon-1235840625%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smoke%20and%20Mirrors%3A%20A%20Tepid%20Parliament%20Session%20That%E2%80%99s%20Turned%20Very%20Hot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15091225%2Fdownload-13.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20as%20many%20as%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%2C%20including%20senior%20ones%20like%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Kanimozhi%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20leader%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%2C%20have%20all%20been%20suspended%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20get%20the%20facts%20clear.%20They%20were%20all%20protesting%20vociferously%20against%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20ensure%20security%20of%20parliament%20on%20December%2013.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20permitting%20those%20who%20burst%20tear-gas%20canisters%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20scot%20free%20till%20the%20time%20of%20writing.%20The%20irony%20is%2C%20however%2C%20that%2015%20Opposition%20MPs%20were%20punished%2C%20on%20the%20majority-party%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20resolution%2C%20for%20shouting%20heated%20slogans%20(defying%20the%20chair)%20and%20demanding%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20the%20home%20minister%20explain%20to%20parliament%20why%20the%20major%20security%20lapse%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20very%20sad%20and%20has%20suddenly%20turned%20a%20tepid%20Delhi%20winter%20and%20a%20pleasantly%20cool%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%20into%20a%20rather%20hot%20one%20%E2%80%94%20just%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%20One%20has%20observed%20that%20every%20recent%20parliament%20session%20often%20becomes%20too%20sizzling%20as%20the%20Opposition%20just%20cannot%20get%20its%20grievances%20across%2C%20without%20outbursts.%20As%20expected%2C%20instead%20of%20soothing%20ruffled%20feathers%2C%20the%20most%20intolerant%20government%20in%20India%20after%20independence%20usually%20exacerbates%20the%20situation.%20It%20uses%20its%20brute%20majority%20to%20steamroll%20dissent%20and%20suspend%20protesters%2C%20and%20a%20self-respecting%20Opposition%20cannot%20gulp%20it%20down%20in%20silence.%20In%20one%20day%2C%20the%20absolute%20calm%20with%20which%20the%20262nd%20session%20began%2C%20and%20continued%20for%20so%20many%20days%2C%20has%20suddenly%20been%20shattered.%20The%20treasury%20benches%20appear%20to%20revel%20not%20only%20in%20dangling%20provocations%20(the%20home%20minister%20could%20jolly%20well%20have%20come%20or%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20have%20spoken%20on%20Manipur)%2C%20but%20also%20seems%20to%20hope%20that%20the%20consequential%20volcanic%20outpourings%20of%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20angst%20somehow%20cross%20the%20red%20line%20%E2%80%94%20so%20that%20they%20could%20display%20their%20might%2C%20by%20imposing%20penalties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20unreal%20calm%20and%20cool%20of%20the%20first%20ten%20days%20was%20actually%20required%20by%20parliamentarians%2C%20irrespective%20of%20party%20poll%2C%20to%20tackle%20and%20negotiate%20the%20unusually%20complex%20architecture%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building.%20True%2C%20members%20had%20undergone%20a%20dress%20rehearsal%20in%20the%20new%20building%20during%20the%20short%20four-day%20%E2%80%98special%20session%E2%80%99%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20summoned%20on%20September%2018.%20Modi%20had%20expected%20the%20session%20to%20celebrate%20the%20shift%20of%20parliament%20from%20the%20old%20building%20to%20the%20new%20nouveau%20riche%20edifice.%20But%20so%20uninspiring%20was%20the%20transition%20that%20MPs%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20stifling%20yawns.%20They%20were%20more%20than%20annoyed%20at%20the%20maze%20within%20the%20new%20House%2C%20replete%20with%20galleries%20that%20showcase%20India%E2%80%99s%20glories%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20incidentally%2C%20occupy%20valuable%20space%20but%20hardly%20get%20visitors.%20The%20second%20reason%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20summoning%20the%20special%20session%20was%20to%20bask%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20what%20he%20considered%20was%20his%20remarkable%20presidentship%20of%20the%20G20%20club.%20But%2C%20here%20again%2C%20except%20a%20few%20die-hard%20sycophants%2C%20no%20one%20even%20mentioned%20the%20imagined%20grandeur%20and%20the%20highly-forgettable%20enforced%20pageantry%20throughout%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-yellow-smoke-signals-tell-us-about-the-mother-of-democracy%5C%22%3EWhat%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-hyped%20but%20disappointingly%20underwhelming%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20confusing%20even%20to%20the%20parliament%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20as%20very%20few%C2%A0%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20new%20building%20before%20inauguration.%20There%20was%20no%20prior%20notice%20to%20MPs%20by%20this%20hush-hush%20regime%3B%20no%20mental%20preparation%2C%20or%20even%20time%20to%20make%20last%20minute%20user-driven%20modifications.%20Hence%2C%20hapless%20parliamentarians%20and%20officials%20are%20now%20burdened%20forever%20(or%20at%20least%20for%20the%20coming%20decades)%20with%20an%20unusually%20complicated%20architecture.%20It%20conveys%20no%20%E2%80%98school%E2%80%99%20of%20architecture%2C%20but%20it%20surely%20reflects%20the%20tastes%20of%20an%20unusually%20aggressive%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20user-friendly%2C%20minion%20architect%20who%20is%20foisted%20with%20duties%20far%20above%20his%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20and%20his%20architect%20have%20cleaved%20parliament%20by%20rendering%20asunder%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20They%20have%20effectively%20erected%20a%20%E2%80%98wall%E2%80%99%20by%20elongating%20and%20complicating%20the%20path%20between%20them.%20The%20previous%20Central%20Hall%2C%20that%20was%20situated%20between%20the%20two%20chambers%2C%20where%20MPs%20from%20both%20Houses%20and%20all%20parties%20could%20meet%20and%20share%20coffee%2C%20snacks%20and%20politics%2C%20has%20now%20been%20eliminated%20%E2%80%93%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20divide%20and%20rule%20policy.%20Even%20the%20common%20canteen%20has%20been%20split%20into%20two%20and%20placed%20wide%20apart%2C%20and%20both%20lack%20grandeur.%20They%20look%20like%20upgraded%20college%20canteens%20or%20mid-market%20cafes.%20The%20regime%E2%80%99s%20insecurity%20ensures%20that%20parliamentarians%20from%20one%20House%20never%20get%20to%20see%20their%20colleagues%20from%20the%20the%20other.%C2%A0%20The%20two%20new%20Houses%20effectively%20convey%20corporate%20distancing%20through%20unnecessarily%20large%20spaces%20(ostensibly%20for%20future%20expansion%20of%20membership)%2C%20and%20have%20surely%20hurt%20the%20proximity%2C%20warmth%20and%20bonhomie%20that%20existed%20in%20the%20previous%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20ceilings%20attempt%20to%20portray%20some%20inexplicable%20architectural%20style%2C%20and%20are%20accompanied%20by%20some%20insipid%20motifs%20and%20garish%20scribbly%20art%20forms.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20high%20ceilings%20combine%20with%20lateral%20distancing%20to%20segregate%20members%2C%20who%20find%20difficulty%20in%20hearing%20what%20is%20being%20said%2C%20with%20using%20headphones.%20To%20many%2C%20marshals%20in%20pink%20coats%20and%20short%20shiny%20turbans%20look%20less%20impressive%20than%20the%20earlier%20ones%20in%20dark%20prince-coats%20and%20flaring%20white%20%3Cem%3Esafa%3C%2Fem%3E-turbans.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20visible%20saffronisation%20of%20dresses%20of%20officials%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20traditional%20default%20colour%20of%20maroon%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20replaced%20with%20a%20colour%20that%20is%20between%20orange%20and%20saffron.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20costume%20designer%20has%20messed%20it%20all%20up%2C%20without%20doubt.%20Appearances%20of%20the%20interior%20of%20parliament%20do%20matter%20a%20lot%20as%20they%20are%20telecast%20throughout%20the%20country%20and%20help%20buttress%20a%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glaring%20nouveau%20riche%20character%20of%20the%20new%20building%20is%20apparent%20everywhere.%20Even%20the%20cheap%20laser-cut%20%3Cem%3Ejalis%3C%2Fem%3E%20affixed%20on%20the%20outer%20walls%20are%20so%20definitely%20inferior%20to%20the%20skilled%20hand-chiselled%20ones%20that%20adorn%20the%20classical%20old%20parliament.%20One%20can%20count%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20Indic%20symbols%20and%20motifs%20in%20the%20colonial%20edifice%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20this%20one%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20neither%20%3Cem%3Edesi%3C%2Fem%3E%20nor%20%3Cem%3Efirangi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20lounges%20are%20surely%20a%20welcome%20addition%2C%20Wi-Fi%20services%20appear%20to%20have%20improved%20and%20the%20personal%20devices%20on%20members%E2%80%99%20tables%20may%20be%20amenable%20to%20better%20utilisation%20if%20they%20came%20with%20computer%20mouses.%20The%20point%20is%20that%20the%20new%20triangular%20building%20will%20remain%20quite%20difficult%20to%20manoeuvre%20and%20the%20clear%20separation%20between%20the%20two%20Houses%20is%20a%20strategic%20trick%20that%20could%20only%20be%20effected%20by%20hegemonic%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20we%20return%20to%20the%20suspensions%2C%20we%20must%20mention%20the%20patently%20unfair%20and%20summary%20manner%20in%20which%20a%20firebrand%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20expelled.%20It%20not%20our%20business%20to%20question%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20chair%20outside%20the%20House%2C%20but%20one%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20clarify%20the%20flow%20of%20events%20beyond%20what%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20patches.%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20expelled%20through%20a%20muscular%20political%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20pre-decided%20plan%2C%20without%20a%20chance%20to%20explain%20her%20side%20and%20without%20any%20discussion%20in%20House.%20Obviously%2C%20this%20has%20led%20to%20an%20uproar%20within%20and%20outside%20parliament%20and%20this%20does%20not%20behove%20well%20for%20the%20highest%20institution%20of%20democracy.%20The%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20that%20prevailed%20in%20the%20first%20week%20was%20shattered%20quite%20rudely%20just%20before%20the%20weekend%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Response%20to%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%20Was%20a%20Bundle%20of%20Contradictions%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-the-govts-response-to-parliament-security-breach-was-a-bundle-of-contradictions%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Response%20to%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%20Was%20a%20Bundle%20of%20Contradictions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20December%2013.%20Twenty-two%20years%20ago%2C%20parliament%20had%20been%20attacked%20by%20terrorists%20and%20on%20this%20very%C2%A0%20unforgettable%20day%2C%20when%20nine%20persons%20had%20lost%20their%20lives.%20The%20prime%20minister%20and%20many%20leaders%20and%20MPs%20assembled%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20pay%20their%20homage%20at%20a%20memorial%20just%20outside%20the%20old%20parliament%20building.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20were%20innumerable%20%E2%80%98photo%20opportunities%E2%80%99.%20But%20then%2C%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20history%20almost%20repeated%20itself%20as%20some%20protesters%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20visitor%E2%80%99s%20gallery%20and%20burst%20canisters%20of%20brightly%20coloured%20%E2%80%98tear%20gas%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20a%20terrible%20violation%20of%20the%20security%20ring%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20protect%20parliament%20and%20one%20shudders%20to%20think%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20they%20had%20burst%20bombs%20or%20grenades%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Members%20were%20visibly%20shaken%20and%20agitated%20%E2%80%94%20but%20neither%20the%20otherwise-articulate%20prime%20minister%20nor%20his%20ever-confident%20home%20minister%20thought%20it%20important%20enough%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20in%20either%20or%20both%20Houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20hitherto-cooperative%20Opposition%20demanded%20their%20presence%20the%20next%20morning%20in%20both%20Houses%20%E2%80%94%20to%20come%20forth%20and%20explain%20what%20it%20had%20done%20so%20far%20and%20planned%20to%20do.%20When%20the%20government%20refused%20to%20show%20any%20light%2C%20heat%20is%20all%20that%20the%20Opposition%20can%20work%20and%20radiate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20face%20yellow%20cards%20and%20red%20cards%20for%20it.%20This%20is%20precisely%20what%20happened%20on%20December%2014.%20In%20a%20show%20of%20unity%2C%20the%20entire%20Opposition%20was%20on%20its%20feet%20demanding%20statements%20from%20the%20government%2C%20but%20it%20happened%20to%20be%20beyond%20the%20decided%20%E2%80%98Business%20of%20the%20House%E2%80%99.%20The%20treasury%20were%20expected%20to%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20had%20done%20in%20the%20past%20with%20forward-looking%20leaders%20like%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20and%20Arun%20Jaitley.%20Instead%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20be%20totally%20intolerant%20of%20discussion%20and%20pounced%20on%20emotional%20outbursts%20of%20the%20Opposition%20to%20ensured%20(through%20their%20majority)%20that%2015%20MPs%20were%20suspended.%20In%20addition%2C%20O%E2%80%99Brien%E2%80%99s%20agitation%20will%20now%20be%20examined%20by%20the%