ctic%2C%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20probe%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20Mediapart%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20information%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20de%20facto%20refused%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20international%20cooperation%20on%20the%20case%20that%20was%20made%20in%20November%202022%20by%20the%20two%20French%20judges%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20criminal%20investigation%20into%20suspected%20%E2%80%9Ccorruption%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cinfluence%20peddling%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfavouritism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20drove%20the%20French%20Embassy%20in%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdistraction%20for%20eight%20months%20before%20ending%20all%20communication%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20French%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Lenain%2C%20who%20is%20now%20France%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20Brazil%2C%20felt%20compelled%20to%20write%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20diplomatic%20note%2C%20he%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20French%20government%20used%20the%20%E2%80%9Copportunity%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20G20%20anti-corruption%20summit%E2%80%9D%20on%20August%2011th%20and%2012th%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20try%20to%20%E2%80%9Cadvance%20certain%20cases%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F060421%2Frafale-jets-sale-india-macron-hollande-and-blind-eye-frances-anti-corruption-services%5C%22%3Ehad%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F140922%2Frafale-papers-french-judges-face-military-secrecy-hurdles-over-probe-sale-fighters%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20the%20French%20and%20Indian%20governments%20are%20united%20in%20their%20desire%20to%20slow%20down%20a%20highly%20sensitive%20investigation%20that%20could%20implicate%20three%20heads%20of%20state%20or%20government%3A%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20French%20president%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20his%20predecessor%20at%20the%20%C3%89lys%C3%A9e%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202018%2C%20the%20French%20investigating%20judges%20had%20requested%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20send%20them%20judicial%20documents%20concerning%20Dassault%20and%20Sushen%20Gupta%2C%20an%20influential%20defence%20businessman%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsushen-gupta-agent-rafale-deal-ed%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20alleged%20Agusta%20Westland%20Chopper%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20was%20also%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20agent%2C%20who%20received%20%E2%80%9Cmillions%20in%20commission%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsushen-gupta-agent-rafale-deal-ed%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freportage%2Fgupta-papers-rafale-deal-agusta-westland-sushen-gupta%5C%22%3Ehad%20also%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20covering%20up%20two%20decades%20of%20defence%20corruption%20to%20save%20the%20Rafale%20deal.%20It%20talked%20about%20h%3Cspan%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message_attachment_text%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3Eow%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20under%20Modi%20had%20evidence%20of%20kickbacks%20in%2015%20major%20defence%20deals%2C%20and%20buried%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-stringify-ignore%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20France%2C%20the%20investigating%20judges%20have%20faced%20two%20refusals%20to%20declassify%20secret%20documents%2C%20many%20of%20which%20they%20came%20across%20during%20a%20search%20of%20French%20defence%20and%20aviation%20company%20Dassault%2C%20%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%20its%20latest%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20as%20earlier%20mentioned%2C%20in%20October%202018%2C%20the%20French%20investigating%20judges%20had%20requested%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20send%20them%20judicial%20documents%20concerning%20Dassault%20and%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20French%20judges%20also%20asked%20for%20two%20searches%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20at%20which%20they%20want%20to%20be%20present%3A%20one%20in%20the%20offices%20of%20one%20of%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20companies%2C%20the%20other%20at%20the%20headquarters%20of%20Dassault%20Reliance%20Aerospace%20Limited%20(DRAL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20joint%20company%20created%20by%20Dassault%20and%20the%20Reliance%20group%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20billionaire%20Anil%20Ambani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20noteworthy%20development%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%20February%202019%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovernment-waived-anti-corruption-clauses-in-rafale-deal%2Farticle61543440.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20removed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Canti-corruption%20clauses%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20in%202016%2C%20just%20before%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20final%20contract.%20This%2C%20despite%20earlier%20objections%20from%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20negotiating%20team%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fdefence%2Fdassault-aviation-seeks-to-buy-out-reliance-stake-in-defence-facility-set-up-100-venture-in-india%2F1672150%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202023%20that%20the%20French%20aviation%20major%20is%20looking%20to%20buy%20out%20the%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20stake%20in%20their%20joint%20venture%2C%20DRAL.%20While%20the%20French%20firm%20owns%20a%2049%25%20stake%20in%20the%20joint%20venture%2C%2051%25%20is%20held%20by%20Reliance%20Defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Dassault%20and%20Reliance%20announced%20their%20joint%20venture%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20DRAL%20on%20October%203%2C%202016%2C%20barely%20two%20weeks%20after%20India%20signed%20the%20Rafale%20deal.%20%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20also%20reported%20how%20Ambani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frafale-corruption-anil-ambani-france-magistrate-tax%5C%22%3Esecured%3C%2Fa%3E%20tax%20reduction%20from%20France%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20latest%20report%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20French%20ambassador%20in%20New%20Delhi%20expressed%20serious%20concern%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20cooperation%20from%20Indian%20authorities%20regarding%20a%20judicial%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20November%2028%2C%202022%2C%20the%20embassy%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20security%20attach%C3%A9%20went%20in%20person%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20meet%20the%20liaison%20judge%20in%20charge%20of%20international%20cooperation%2C%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20request%20from%20the%20French%20judges.%20It%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20the%20ministry%20by%20courier%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20liaison%20judge%20did%20not%20get%20back%20in%20touch%20for%20two%20months%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20on%20February%206%2C%202023%2C%20he%20informed%20the%20French%20authorities%20that%20he%20%5Bthe%20liaison%20judge%5D%20had%20been%20moved%20to%20another%20position%20and%20was%20not%20being%20immediately%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20ambassador%2C%20Emmanuel%20Lenain%2C%20became%20impatient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%20his%20second%20in%20command%20and%20his%20domestic%20security%20attach%C3%A9%20managed%20to%20meet%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20director%20in%20charge%20of%20international%20affairs%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20person%20in%20charge%20of%20Franco-Indian%20relations%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20officials%20promised%20that%20they%20would%20respond%20to%20the%20French%20judges%E2%80%99%20request%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20Embassy%20discovered%20on%20April%2024%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20had%20finally%20appointed%20a%20new%20liaison%20judge%20responsible%20for%20handling%20requests%20for%20cooperation%20on%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20being%20contacted%2C%20the%20latter%20has%20never%20responded%20to%20our%20requests.%20Yet%20his%20appointment%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20in%20an%20email%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023%20which%20was%20received%20by%20the%20domestic%20security%20attach%C3%A9%20who%20once%20again%20sought%20to%20contact%20this%20judge%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20ambassador%20Lenain%20in%20his%20diplomatic%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%2C%20per%20the%20report%2C%20illustrates%20in%20particular%20the%20desire%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20echoed%20in%20Paris%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20French%20judicial%20investigation%20into%20corruption%20over%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20Rafale%20jets%20does%20not%20reach%20an%20outcome.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20the%20investigating%20judges%20face%20a%20major%20hurdle%2C%20as%20they%20lack%20both%20the%20classified%20French%20documents%20and%20the%20Indian%20judicial%20documents%20which%20prove%20the%20payment%20of%20secret%20commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20are%20also%20facing%20challenges%20with%20regard%20to%20this%20case%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20%C3%89liane%20Houlette%2C%20then%20head%20of%20France%E2%80%99s%20financial%20crimes%20prosecution%20unit%2C%20dismissed%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20anti-corruption%20NGO%20Sherpa%2C%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20one%20of%20her%20deputies%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpreserve%20France%E2%80%99s%20interests%E2%80%9D.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20until%20June%202021%20that%20a%20judge-led%20investigation%20was%20initiated%2C%20prompted%20by%20a%20second%20complaint%20from%20Sherpa%20based%20on%20revelations%20from%20Mediapart%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Rafale%20Papers%E2%80%99%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20communications%20service%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702575829000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F01113703%2FEx0y648U4AEQxnO.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-govt-stonewalls-rafale-deal-corruption-probe-by-french-judges-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20dated%20July%2025%2C%202023%2C%20French%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Emmanuel%20Lenain%20highlighted%20difficulties%20in%20collaborating%20on%20criminal%20cases%20with%20India.%20He%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20cases%20are%20handled%20by%20our%20Indian%20partners%20with%20very%20long%20delays%2C%20often%20in%20an%20incomplete%20manner.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A113%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-govt-stonewalls-rafale-deal-corruption-probe-by-french-judges-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Another%20Death%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Day%20that%20Bodies%20Lying%20in%20Morgues%20Were%20Finally%20Returned%20to%20Kin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14230428%2Fimage-1611.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20sensitive%20border%20state%20which%20has%20been%20riven%20with%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20since%20May%203%2C%20saw%20another%20death%20on%20Thursday%2C%20December%2014%2C%20when%20a%2026-year-old%20Kuki%20volunteer%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Haolenphai%20Tengnoupal%20district%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaitinmang%20Baite%20was%20killed%20on%20the%20day%20when%20the%20bodies%20of%20both%20communities%20(Meitei%20and%20Kuki)%2C%20which%20were%20lying%20in%20the%20morgues%20of%20different%20districts%20of%20Manipur%2C%20were%20finally%20sent%20to%20their%20respective%20districts.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Baite%E2%80%99s%20aunt%2C%20Hoilhing%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20final%20year%20student%20doing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree.%20He%20has%20three%20children%20and%20the%20youngest%20is%20just%20a%20week%20old.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20he%20received%20%E2%80%9Cfour-five%20bullet%20injuries%20before%20finally%20succumbing%20to%20injuries%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%20hospital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-dead-unclaimed%5C%22%3Eordered%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20bury%20the%20unidentified%20and%20unclaimed%20bodies%20of%20individuals%20killed%20during%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20that%20has%20been%20effectively%20not%20in%20control%20for%20over%20seven%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased%20can%20accept%20the%20bodies%20and%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20at%20any%20of%20the%20nine%20burial%20sites%20identified%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20or%20the%20state%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20the%20same%20in%20accordance%20with%20municipal%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20had%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inability%20of%20family%20members%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20state%20to%20collect%20the