uting%20slogans%20against%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cdictatorship%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country%2C%20even%20as%20police%20personnel%20held%20her.%20Reports%20which%20cite%20the%20initial%20police%20probe%20indicate%20that%20they%20believed%20that%20their%20attack%20on%20the%20Parliament%20was%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20political%20class%20to%20discuss%20issues%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-understanding-indias-unemployment-rate-with-economist-arun-kumar%5C%22%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ftax-as-confiscation-modi-governments-k-shaped-policy-proves-keynes-right%5C%22%3Eprice%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3Eunending%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fits-more-than-an-agrarian-crisis-p-sainath%2Farticle28122414.ece%5C%22%3Eagrarian%20distress%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20six%2C%20four%20of%20them%20have%20already%20been%20held.%20One%20of%20them%20shot%20a%20video%20of%20his%20partners%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20political%20class%2C%20again%2C%20mostly%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20circulate%20it%20widely%2C%20and%20fled.%20Of%20the%20six%20of%20them%2C%20two%20are%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20Parliamentary%20premises%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20were%20those%20who%20were%20held%20shouting%20slogans%20outside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20and%20their%20associates%20Lalit%20Jha%20and%20Vicky%20Sharma.%20As%20is%20evident%2C%20they%20belong%20to%20different%20regions%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20say%20that%20the%20group%20were%20followers%20of%20a%20social%20media%20group%20called%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club%2C%20and%20were%20attempting%20to%20emulate%20the%20Indian%20