%99t%20hard.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20am%20going%20with%20music%20full-time%20and%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240763%2Fnagaland-shiitake-oyster-mushrooms-earns-lakhs-how-to-grow-spores-method-scientist-innovation-agritech-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimapur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%20that%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20make%20my%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nagaland's%20growing%20Hip%20Hop%20community%20has%20Moko%20Koza%20at%20the%20front%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoko%20Koza%20receiving%20the%20TaFMA%20Excellence%20Award%20(Left)%3B%20At%20a%20location%20for%20his%20music%20video%20(Right)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAse%20emi%20ekt