20he%20harboured%20a%20persistent%20interest%20in%20starting%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EleFant%20emerged%20from%20the%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20toys%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20brand%20for%20parents%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-7-1700662736-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20in%2014%20cities%20so%20far.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20The%20EleFant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20changing%20family%20dynamics%2C%20Sourabh%20observed%20the%20increasing%20challenge%20for%20parents%20who%20juggle%20work%20and%20home%20responsibilities%20simultaneously.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I%20would%20be%20working%2C%20leaving%20little%20room%20to%20go%20out%20and%20search%20for%20toys.%20I%20wanted%20to%20simplify%20one%20thing%20for%20working%20parents%20like%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20the%20corporate%20world%20for%20Sourabh%20was%20gradual.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20began%20taking%20shape%20in%20my%20mind%20in%202022%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20a%20solid%20plan%20of%20action.%20I%20aimed%20to%20offer%20parents%20a%20reliable%20service%20and%20an%20effective%20subscription%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20ensuring%20that%20the%20toys%20provided%20to%20children%20are%20not%20just%20enjoyable%20but%20also%20engaging%20and%20educational.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20understand%20how%20crucial%20it%20is%20for%20kids%20to%20have%20the%20right%20environment%20at%20the%20right%20time%20to%20encourage%20them%20and%20help%20them%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20this%20concept%2C%20Sourabh%20enlisted%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173434%2Fkerala-free-mental-health-care-doctor-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpertise%20of%20a%20psychologist%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20paediatrician%20and%20an%20ex-school%20principal%20to%20discern%20the%20types%20of%20toys%20that%20would%20be%20most%20beneficial%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20developing%20the%20concept%20and%20ensuring%20that%20all%20our%20toys%20meet%20the%20highest%20quality%20standards%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20launch%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20of%20more%20than%20250%20subscribers%20with%20over%202%2C000%20downloads%20of%20the%20application%20per%20day.%20They%20also%20have%20collaborations%20with%2070%20toy%20companies%20where%20they%20source%20their%20toys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20250%20subscribers%20is%20Rahul%20Bhauwala%20from%20Mumbai%20who%20rents%20toys%20for%20his%206-year-old.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20working%20professional%20and%20I%20hardly%20get%20any%20time%20to%20go%20out%20and%20spend%20hours%20looking%20for%20and%20buying%20toys.%20I%20could%20use%20that%20precious%20time%20to%20play%20with%20my%20child%20instead.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20love%20using%20The%20EleFant%20app.%20They%20have%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20toys%20which%20are%20categorised%20as%20per%20age.%20The%20products%20are%20very%20well-packaged%20and%20my%20son%20loved%20opening%20them%20as%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20present%20to%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20circular%20economy%20where%20toys%20are%20reused%20repeatedly.%20This%20not%20only%20cuts%20costs%20but%20also%20benefits%20the%20environment.%20Considering%20how%20quickly%20kids%20outgrow%20things%2C%20toys%20often%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPocket-friendly%20for%20parents%20and%20fun%20for%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20habit%20of%20reusing%20and%20thrifting%20might%20have%20started%20trending%20recently%2C%20if%20we%20look%20back%20to%20our%20childhood%2C%20sharing%20children%E2%80%99s%20belongings%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20pass%20down%20our%20toys%20and%20clothes%20to%20our%3Cem%3E%20chachi%2C%20mami%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(aunts)%20kids.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20nuclear%20family%20setup%2C%20this%20trend%20has%20declined.%20I%20think%20it%20was%20this%20practice%20that%20has%20made%20people%20place%20their%20trust%20in%20us%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20reaction%20of%20the%20people%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20were%20very%20delighted%20and%20showed%20encouragement.%20While%20they%20were%20a%20little%20sceptical%20of%20sanitation%20since%20these%20products%20will%20be%20reused%2C%20I%20explained%20that%20we%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3